test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x755b80a0a680>([-17])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x755b80a0a680> = [[1, -17], [1, -17, 1], [-17], [-17, 1], [1, -17], [1, -17, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 17 == -17
 +  where 17 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -17])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
